- So you have to install react from browser

- Open VS code and there is terminal option open and go to new terminal

- Type command

-Choose the name : npx create-react-app my-app

-Change directory : cd my-app ( app name )

-Run : npm start

-If it is correct it will show happy hacking like that

Once done 

Open src check which code I gave you, just edit or replace with my code 

After that when you save automatically it will run 

